   <body xml:lang="eng">
      <div n="1" type="sententia">
         <div n="1" type="ln">Love the Lord
            and he will love you;</div>
         <div n="2" type="ln">and serve him,
            and he will enlighten your heart.</div>
      </div>
      <div n="2" type="sententia">
         <div n="1" type="ln">Honor your mother as the mother of Christ,</div>
         <div n="2" type="ln">and do not irritate the grey head of her who bore you.</div>
      </div>
      <div n="3" type="sententia">
         <div n="1" type="ln">Love your sisters as the daughters of your mother,</div>
         <div n="2" type="ln">and do not abandon the way of peace.</div>
      </div>
      <div n="4" type="sententia">
         <div n="1" type="ln">May the rising sun see the Book in your hands,</div>
         <div n="2" type="ln">and after the second hour your work.</div>
      </div>
      <div n="5" type="sententia">
         <div n="1" type="ln">Pray ceaselessly</div>
         <div n="2" type="ln">and remember Christ who begot you.</div>
      </div>
      <div n="6" type="sententia">
         <div n="1" type="ln">Avoid incidents involving men, </div>
         <div n="2" type="ln">so that images do not arise in your soul;</div>
         <div n="3" type="ln">for they will be a stumbling block for you at the time of prayer.</div>
      </div>
      <div n="7" type="sententia">
         <div n="1" type="ln">Christ you have as [your] beloved:</div>
         <div n="2" type="ln">cast away from you all men;</div>
         <div n="3" type="ln">and you will not live a shameful life.</div>
      </div>
      <div n="8" type="sententia">
         <div n="1" type="ln">Put indignation and anger far away from you,</div>
         <div n="2" type="ln">and do not let brooding over injury lodge within you.</div>
      </div>
      <div n="9" type="sententia">
         <div n="1" type="ln">Do not say, “Today I will eat but I will not eat tomorrow,”</div>
         <div n="2" type="ln">for you do not do this with prudence.</div>
         <div n="3" type="ln">Indeed, this will cause harm to your body</div>
         <div n="4" type="ln">and pain in your stomach.</div>
      </div>
      <div n="10" type="sententia">
         <div n="1" type="ln">Eating meat is not decent, nor is drinking wine good;</div>
         <div n="2" type="ln">these should rather be offered to the sick.</div>
      </div>
      <div n="11" type="sententia">
         <div n="1" type="ln">The rash virgin will not be saved;</div>
         <div n="2" type="ln">the wanton will not see her bridegroom.</div>
      </div>
      <div n="15" type="sententia">
         <div n="1" type="ln">Open your mouth with the word of God, </div>
         <div n="2" type="ln">and restrain your tongue from prolixity.</div>
      </div>
